{"tid":1587953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「行動post」 號召1000位巴絲 《網上罷食美心》23及24號","createTime":"2019-09-22T15:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T17:51:48.000Z","uid":112769,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"62ad3ebbcfd1f30f1a1665888c9e22da54e01ddd","tid":1587953,"uid":112769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:31:44.000Z","msg":"今次的網上號召1000名巴絲打 係想透過極低成本去提高藍絲食肆的行政成本 再影響佢地的生意額 最終影響到佢地收皮執笠<br />\n<br />\n依個想法係來自今日有手足去翠園禁哂d飛諗出黎 應該係話果位巴打的2.0版本<br />\n<br />\n係全部新鴻基地產旗下的購物商場都可以<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">透過「apps 網上拎飛仔」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zxG953x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzxG953x.png&h=01836e59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pkq3q3F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPkq3q3F.png&h=09b02bfb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oQJDZoG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoQJDZoG.png&h=9407cf11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁樣姐係話 只要大家係新鴻基個apps入邊搵到一間藍店 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CTrVhau.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCTrVhau.png&h=e92a7590&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你就可以直接拎飛仔拎籌排隊 <br />\n每一部手機 只可以係同一間鋪入邊拎一次飛仔 叫過左5個號 你將飛仔就會自動取消 可以再拎多次 而你係可以一次過拎哂咁多間唔同鋪頭的飛仔 但係一間鋪拎得一張<br />\n<br />\n你可能會問 拎得一次有q用咩？<br />\n你咁諗法大錯特錯了<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1張飛仔大約要用6秒鐘叫一次號<br />\n你600張飛仔就要用1個鐘頭黎叫號<br />\n如果動員到1000人去咁做</span></span><br />\n佢果日基本上可以唔洗做生意<br />\n試諗一下 你見到叫緊103號飛仔時<br />\n但你手上果張已經排到509號<br />\n你仲會唔會排隊入去食？<br />\n<br />\n當然啦佢地取消個網上飛仔 代唔代表我地行動失敗？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">No no no</span></span>佢地就算取消左網上拎飛<br />\n但係影響到一堆利用開飛仔系統的人 因為唔方便而唔再去食 或 小左去食<br />\n咁我地的計劃就已經係成功左<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2kgaQvA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2kgaQvA.png&h=76690007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">行動日期：9月23及24號<br />\n行動時間：12:00-13:30 18:00-20:30<br />\n目標商場：新都會商場<br />\n目標食店：潮庭 北京樓 simplylife<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">罷食藍店 你我有責</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時期革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"d705482903573f619850fdbe63edf56572be0447","tid":1587953,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:31:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"1213c55012438ee7815fd47b3d96602d12126da5","tid":1587953,"uid":112769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:33:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf0eac0f6b350e446f0a810e384a2166811a78e","tid":1587953,"uid":112769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b66f1b2cbe01443c3527d9e6538952f88d27975","tid":1587953,"uid":112769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:33:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a48a69cedf70c070e4420dbc3109843714e9bc9","tid":1587953,"uid":295124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T15:34:31.000Z","msg":"手機apps會唔會trace到個主人"},{"pid":"7ef08a05415ec9e796381149353a133134df866c","tid":1587953,"uid":112769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a48a69cedf70c070e4420dbc3109843714e9bc9","tid":1587953,